it.polimi.ingsw.ps42.model

Class CardTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps42.model.CardTest

  • public class CardTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class tests the main functionalities of the Card class: it creates some Cards and tries to pay them with different Players and then tries to enable their effects; also tests some lateral functionalities such as the cloning method, the getters and the show method
    Author:
    Luca Napoletano, Claudio Montanari
